{
  "texts": [
    "Increased Payload Capacity: Commercial drones typically have weight limitations for safety reasons.",
    "However, by modifying the drone's structure or adding stronger motors, it can carry a heavier payload.",
    "This allows for the transportation of larger and potentially dangerous objects.",
    "Enhanced Speed and Maneuverability: Aggressive drones may be modified to achieve higher speeds and improved maneuverability.",
    "This enables them to quickly approach targets or evade countermeasures, making them more effective in carrying out aggressive acts."
  ]
}